{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 17''' is the 17th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kōhei|ja|康平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1062|ja|1062nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Zenkyū War|ja|前九年の役|lt=Former Nine Years' War|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} concluded{{要出典|date=2021-04}} . {{ill|Minamoto Yoriyoshi|ja|源頼義|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} defeated {{ill|Abe Sadanari|ja|安倍貞任|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} at the {{ill|Chugawa Barrier|ja|厨川柵|lt=Chugawa Barrier|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – Japan’s first Western-style {{ill|lighthouse|ja|灯台|lt=lighthouse|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} began construction at {{ill|Kannonzaki|ja|観音崎|lt=Kannonzaki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Empō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1675|ja|1675th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|lt=Satsuma Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1689|ja|1689th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshi-michi|ja|徳川吉通|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|lt=Owari Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Masaoka Shiki|ja|正岡子規|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|lt=haiku poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|waka poet|ja|歌人|lt=waka poet|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1902|ja|1902nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Masatsugu|ja|石田正継|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|sengoku military commander|ja|武将|lt=sengoku military commander|lt_ja=戦国武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (birth year unknown).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Kannamesai|ja|神嘗祭|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Moved to {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} after the adoption of the New Calendar)
