'''September 17''' is the 17th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . 
