* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – Japan’s first Western-style {{ill|lighthouse|ja|灯台|lt=lighthouse|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  began construction at {{ill|Kannonzaki|ja|観音崎|lt=Kannonzaki|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .

