== Births == * {{ill|Empō|ja|延宝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1675|ja|1675th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|lt=Satsuma Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (died {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1689|ja|1689th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshi-michi|ja|徳川吉通|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|lt=Owari Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (died {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Masaoka Shiki|ja|正岡子規|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|lt=haiku poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and {{ill|waka poet|ja|歌人|lt=waka poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (died {{ill|1902|ja|1902nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Masatsugu|ja|石田正継|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a {{ill|sengoku military commander|ja|武将|lt=sengoku military commander|lt_ja=戦国武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (birth year unknown).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Kannamesai|ja|神嘗祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Moved to {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} after the adoption of the New Calendar)
