'''September 17''' is the 17th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Kōhei|ja|康平|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  5th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1062|ja|1062nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Zenkyū War|ja|前九年の役|lt=Former Nine Years' War|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  concluded{{要出典|date=2021-04|qq=}} . {{ill|Minamoto Yoriyoshi|ja|源頼義|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  defeated {{ill|Abe Sadanari|ja|安倍貞任|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  at the {{ill|Chugawa Barrier|ja|厨川柵|lt=Chugawa Barrier|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – Japan’s first Western-style {{ill|lighthouse|ja|灯台|lt=lighthouse|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  began construction at {{ill|Kannonzaki|ja|観音崎|lt=Kannonzaki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} .

== Births ==
* {{ill|Empō|ja|延宝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1675|ja|1675th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|lt=Satsuma Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (died {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1689|ja|1689th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshi-michi|ja|徳川吉通|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|lt=Owari Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (died {{ill|1713|ja|1713rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1867|ja|1867th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Masaoka Shiki|ja|正岡子規|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|lt=haiku poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  and {{ill|waka poet|ja|歌人|lt=waka poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (died {{ill|1902|ja|1902nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Masatsugu|ja|石田正継|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , a {{ill|sengoku military commander|ja|武将|lt=sengoku military commander|lt_ja=戦国武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (birth year unknown).

== Commemorations ==
* {{ill|Kannamesai|ja|神嘗祭|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  (Moved to {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}  after the adoption of the New Calendar)

