{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 17일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 17''' is the 17th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kōhei|ja|康平|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōhei|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1062|ja|1062nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1062|qq=}} {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 22|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Zenkyū War|ja|前九年の役|lt=Former Nine Years' War|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zenkyū War|qq=}} concluded{{Citation needed|date=2021-04|qq=}} . {{ill|Minamoto Yoriyoshi|ja|源頼義|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto Yoriyoshi|qq=}} defeated {{ill|Abe Sadanari|ja|安倍貞任|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Abe Sadanari|qq=}} at the {{ill|Chugawa Barrier|ja|厨川柵|lt=Chugawa Barrier|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chugawa Barrier|qq=}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 1|qq=}} ) – Japan’s first Western-style {{ill|lighthouse|ja|灯台|lt=lighthouse|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/lighthouse|qq=}} began construction at {{ill|Kannonzaki|ja|観音崎|lt=Kannonzaki|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannonzaki|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Empō|ja|延宝|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empō|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1675|ja|1675年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1675|qq=}} {{ill|November 4|ja|11月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 4|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Yoshitaka|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Satsuma Domain|ja|薩摩藩|lt=Satsuma Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Satsuma Domain|qq=}} (died {{ill|1747|ja|1747年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1747|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1689|ja|1689年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1689|qq=}} {{ill|October 29|ja|10月29日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 29|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshi-michi|ja|徳川吉通|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yoshi-michi|qq=}} , the 4th lord of the {{ill|Owari Domain|ja|尾張藩|lt=Owari Domain|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Owari Domain|qq=}} (died {{ill|1713|ja|1713年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1713|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 3rd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1867|ja|1867年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1867|qq=}} {{ill|October 14|ja|10月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 14|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Masaoka Shiki|ja|正岡子規|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Masaoka Shiki|qq=}} , a {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|lt=haiku poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=}} and {{ill|waka poet|ja|歌人|lt=waka poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/waka poet|qq=}} (died {{ill|1902|ja|1902nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1902|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 23|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Masatsugu|ja|石田正継|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ishida Masatsugu|qq=}} , a {{ill|sengoku military commander|ja|武将|lt=sengoku military commander|lt_ja=戦国武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/sengoku military commander|qq=}} (birth year unknown).
