namoto no Yoriyoshi|Minamoto Yoriyoshi]] defeated [[:en:Abe no Sadato|Abe Sadanari]] at the {{ill|Chugawa Barrier|ja|厨川柵|lt=Chugawa Barrier|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chugawa Barrier|qq=|1=Kuriyagawa Stockade|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11410106}} . * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ) – Japan’s first Western-style [[:en:Lighthouse|lighthouse]] began construction at [[:en:Cape Kannon|Kannonzaki]] .
== Births == * [[:en:Enpō|Empō]] 3rd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1675|1675]] [[:en:November 4|November 4]] ) – {{ill|Shimazu Yoshitaka|ja|島津吉貴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimazu Yoshitaka|qq=|1=Shimazu Yoshitaka|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11246537}} , the 4th lord of the [[:en:Satsuma Domain|Satsuma Domain]] (died [[:en:1747|1747]] ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 2nd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1689|1689]] [[:en:October 29|October 29]] ) – [[:en:Tokugawa Yoshimichi|Tokugawa Yoshi-michi]] , the 4th lord of the [[:en:Owari Domain|Owari Domain]] (died [[:en:1713|1713]] ). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 3rd Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1867|1867]] [[:en:October 14|October 14]] ) – [[:en:Masaoka Shiki|Masaoka Shiki]] , a {{ill|haiku poet|ja|Haiku Poet|lt=haiku poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/haiku poet|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} and {{ill|waka poet|ja|歌人|lt=waka poet|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/waka poet|qq=}} (died [[:en:1902|1902]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Keichō|Keichō]] 5th Year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1600|1600]] [[:en:October 23|October 23]] ) – [[:en:Ishida Masatsugu|Ishida Masatsugu]] , a {{ill|sengoku military commander|ja|武将|lt=sengoku military commander|lt_ja=戦国武将|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/sengoku military commander|qq=|1=military commander|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11545923}} (birth year unknown).
